accessor_requires_borrow_and_mutate_accessors
borrow_inout_experimental
experimental_macro
lifetime_dependence_cannot_use_parsed_scoped_consuming
lifetime_dependence_ctor_non_self_or_nil_return
lifetime_dependence_invalid_init_return
make_inverse_conditional_non_requirement_explicit
make_inverse_conditional_requirement_explicit
perf_hint_param_expects_existential
regionbasedisolation_closure_captures
regionbasedisolation_merge_region_failure_error_functionisolation_sil
remark_scanner_uncached_lookups
sil_operand_has_incompatible_ownership_kind
